ter" style="color:#3A95FF">flags</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       Optional flags, unused for now.      </p>     </dd>       </dl>  </span> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-ziparchive.setmtimeindex-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   成功时返回 <strong><span>true</span></strong>， 或者在失败时返回 <strong><span>false</span></strong>。  </p> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-ziparchive.setmtimeindex-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>    <span>     This example creates a ZIP file archive     <var class="filename">test.zip</var> and add     the file <var class="filename">test.txt</var>     with its modification date.    </span>    <div class="example" id="example-2609">     <p><strong>示例 #1 Archive a file</strong></p>     <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />$zip </span><span style="color: #007700">= new </span><span style="color: #9876AA">ZipArchive</span><span style="color: #007700">();<br />if (</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$zip</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">open</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'test.zip'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">ZipArchive</span><span style="color: #007700">::</span><span style="color: #9876AA">CREATE</span><span style="color: #007700">) === </span><span style="color: #9876AA">TRUE</span><span style="color: #007700">) {<br />    </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$zip</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">addFile</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'text.txt'</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />    </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$zip</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">setMtimeIndex</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">mktime</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">,</span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">,</span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">,</span><span style="color: #9876AA">12</span><span style="color: #007700">,</span><span style="color: #9876AA">25</span><span style="color: #007700">,</span><span style="color: #9876AA">2019</span><span style="color: #007700">));<br />    </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$zip</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">close</span><span style="color: #007700">();<br />    echo </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Ok\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br />} else {<br />    echo </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"KO\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br />}<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></span></div>     </div>    </div> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 notes" id="refsect1-ziparchive.setmtimeindex-notes">  <h3 class="title">注释</h3>  <blockquote class="note" style="border:1px gray solid"><p><strong class="note" style="border:1px gray solid">注意</strong>:    <p class="para">    This function is only available if built against libzip ≥ 1.0.0.   </p>  </p></blockquote> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-ziparchive.setmtimeindex-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link ZipArchive::setMtimeName()} - Set the modification time of an entry defined by its name</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
